title: Ghostbusters & Ghostbusters II 720p HDTV
description:
From rutracker.

Ghostbusters (1984) uses same colour grading as the 1999 DVD. The quality is not excellent and the end credits are missing (after Slimer "eats" the screen) but if you prefer the overall look of the 1999 DVD then this is a worthy upgrade.


Ghostbusters II (1989) uses same color grading as the 2005 DVD, which has more vibrant colours than the 1999 DVD.

Both films have English and Russian audio
